Ppatmod

superclass: Pattern


the function that modifies the enclosed pattern and embeds it in the stream.

Ppatmod(pattern, func, repeats)


 
(
a = Ppatmod(
 Pseq([0, 0, 0, 0],1),
 { arg pat, i;
 var list;
 list = pat.list;
 pat.list = list.put(list.size.rand, 2);
 }, inf);

x = a.asStream;
30.do({ x.next.postln });
)


